  "description": [
    "LOCAL MENTION Quite a number of children are ill with mumps Mrs A R Sparks is spending a few days in Ogden We have had a touch of real win ter weather the past week Miss Lizzie Morgan has accepted a position at the U P store at Nd 4 Mr and Mrs Harry Hougard have been enjoying a visit in Denver the past week Dan Ganiard is In Detroit Mich in the interests of the Western Auto Transit Co Mrs Dora Love has been ill the past week at the home of her aunt Mrs George Brown Bishop Thomas confirmed a class of seven at the Church of the Holy Communion last Sunday A little daughter arrived at the home of Mr and Mrs John Mc Mahan on Friday Nov 6th Mr and Mrs Ed Anesi have re turned home after spending some time at their ranch near Lander Mr and Mrs V J Facinelli and Mr and Mrs P C Bunning have been Ogden visitors the past week Miss Dorothy VanDeusen has been in Kemmerer this week where she attended the Armistice Day dance NECESSITIES SERVICE and COURTESY tAuto Supply Company SIS c st ock Springs Wyo For"
